                    <span>Good book.  Read it after listening to the interview<br>on First Voice.  Detailed, specific, thoughtful.<p>The interview is online at<br>http://www.7to7.net/zim.html<p>There's a transcript for those using dial up.<p>--J. R.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great insight..</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
